data.description: This beautiful luxurious home in the Heron Bay Golf & Country Club is waiting for you!. The home layout is open and inviting, has 5 bedrooms and 4 full bathrooms, with a bedroom on the main level. Also, there's a bonus room with a closet that can be used as a 6th bedroom. The breathtaking serene neighborhood is welcoming as you drive through. If you are fitness-conscious, here is a place to walk, swim, and play tennis and golf. Hurry! This one won't last! Motivated seller! Bring all offers!
